      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "主线用main，功能分支叫newbranch。标题我想写成'Merge feature to advanced main (bottom-to-top)'，强调这是高级用法。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "title",
