      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先初始化图结构，设置BT方向，然后从main的第一个提交开始。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "gitGraph BT",
        "commit",
        "main"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "流程应该是：main先有一个初始提交，然后切出newbranch做开发，同时main也继续往前走一个提交，最后把newbranch合并回来。这样能看到真正的并行开发场景。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "checkout newbranch",
        "commit",
        "checkout main",
