      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "明白了，我按这个顺序画：main初始commit，branch newbranch，切过去commit，切回main再commit，最后merge newbranch。这样合并点会在最上面。",
      "elements_involved": [
